        <a href="#calendar" class="glass-morphism px-10 py-5 3xl:px-16 3xl:py-8 4xl:px-24 4xl:py-12 rounded-full font-black text-lg 3xl:text-2xl 4xl:text-4xl border border-white/10 uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-white/5 transition-all">VIEW EVENTS</a>
